rows.label: qst006501_msg0001
rows.name:
A Whelzaman Cookie, for me? Sorry,
I don't feel like one right now...

rows.label: qst006501_msg0002
rows.name:
That nasty Janiki stole my
favorite treasure from me...

rows.label: qst006501_msg0003
rows.name:
Without my treasure, I don't
feel like eating anything!

rows.label: qst006501_msg0004
rows.name:
Th-thanks! I think Janiki was
heading over towards Loska's Gap.

rows.label: qst006501_msg1001
rows.name:
You'll get my treasure
back from Janiki, right?

rows.label: qst006501_msg1002
rows.name:
I think Janiki was heading
over towards Loska's Gap.

rows.label: qst006501_msg2001
rows.name: Ahhh! It's my treasure! Thank you!

rows.label: qst006501_msg2002
rows.name:
Now I might have the appetite for
one of those Whelzaman Cookies!

rows.label: qst006501_msg3001
rows.name:
When I grow up, I wanna
marry a girl who makes the
BEST Whelzaman Cookies.
